AboutText:
Volleyball School 25;23 - a family where everyone is united by love for volleyball, warm atmosphere of acceptance, support and care. 

We aim at the all-round development of the personality - physical, spiritual, intellectual, social and mental, and our main value - people. That is why our training process includes not only sessions in the gym, but also additional meetings, trips and tournaments.
